d 'MKTEX': module to convert Microsoft Word (.docx) documents to LaTeX (.tex) format with complete document structure
d
d	mktex converts Microsoft Word (.docx) documents to complete
d LaTeX (.tex) documents with table of	  contents support.  The
d command creates a full LaTeX document structure including
d preamble, packages,	 and proper document formatting.  It is
d optimized for both Chinese and English documents, with   
d automatic language detection and appropriate package selection.  
d  The generated LaTeX document includes a table of contents that
d is properly linked in the PDF output.    For Chinese documents,
d the command automatically includes the ctex package and sets
d appropriate	 fonts. 
d
d KW: document
d KW: docx
d KW: LaTeX
d KW: Chinese text
d
d Requires: Stata version 18 and pandoc from pandoc.org
d
d Distribution-Date: 20260206
d
d Author: Wu LiangHai,  Anhui University of Technology
